{"tid":1848201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"行動po,有個職業大家忽略咗...比起129醫護罷工更重要！」","createTime":"2020-01-28T10:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T12:43:35.000Z","uid":288018,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a89019aa63b609553b62a042575c797e51167a64","tid":1848201,"uid":288018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:38:45.000Z","msg":"首先咩職業最能夠憾動到政權？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「運輸業司機、金融業、物流業、航空業」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n尤其係公共交通嘅司機們係重點！<br />\n<br />\n其實一直嘅罷工行動，以上嘅職業如果有6成人出嚟，堅持一個星期，已經可以令一個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">政府倒台</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n和理非行動，「罷工係和理非最激進亦係最溫和嘅抗爭手段」，只要夠多人夠齊心上下一心肯放棄搵幾日錢嘅人工，甚至唔需要rb、唔需要裝修，都可以令一個城市癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n特別<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>香港係國際金融中心</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n今次可唔可以阻止到香港疫症爆發，或者未來可唔可以達到五大訴求，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>129罷工行動好重要。</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實香港除咗係中共嘅春袋之外，更加貼切形容，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港係中共嘅「心臟」～</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n好多同路人未了解香港有幾值錢，仍然戀慕緊個制度可以贏，想搶攻功能組別，錯失談判良機，忽視左真普選令香港重光機會。<br />\n<br />\n若果，生命同埋返工之間，最後都係要揀返工嘅話，都冇嘢好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/28/183800_1b9f557e034c1b1ca5191634c770a29c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F28%2F183800_1b9f557e034c1b1ca5191634c770a29c.jpeg&h=e883dc90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/28/183801_b8ae3e49e47dcb55f6ef4239d88c1ebe.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F28%2F183801_b8ae3e49e47dcb55f6ef4239d88c1ebe.jpeg&h=36e09051&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/28/183802_121cdc8e1db5a8e6589f4f32fa55bd71.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F28%2F183802_121cdc8e1db5a8e6589f4f32fa55bd71.jpeg&h=9da27924&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/28/183803_728e5cff9f4f016c7cac947407fe2154.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F28%2F183803_728e5cff9f4f016c7cac947407fe2154.jpeg&h=0e0b7d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/28/183804_2d1d49a13ae51eb6a4b92c5714eb4be1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F28%2F183804_2d1d49a13ae51eb6a4b92c5714eb4be1.jpeg&h=24fb991b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/28/183805_a5a6e4b632eacef625c3f7ca7ebdaae3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F28%2F183805_a5a6e4b632eacef625c3f7ca7ebdaae3.jpeg&h=e0dcfaa3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/28/183806_fb53bc903d6b20f03d4942ba26cced02.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F28%2F183806_fb53bc903d6b20f03d4942ba26cced02.jpeg&h=bc1e16bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/28/183807_19965b6105c71df3e79d08505d465c2c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F28%2F183807_19965b6105c71df3e79d08505d465c2c.jpeg&h=d5373445&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/28/183807_ced104ce966947e5814e224889e8fcd0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F28%2F183807_ced104ce966947e5814e224889e8fcd0.jpeg&h=1b674a86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"ht